Package: jeva
Type: Package
Title: Evidential Analyses for Common Statistical Tests
Version: 0.0.7
Author: Peter Cahusac
Maintainer: Peter Cahusac <peteqsac@gmail.com>
Description: Analyses that calculate the log likelihood (support) for a 
    range of statistical tests. Where possible the likelihood
    function and support interval for the observed data are displayed.
    Intended as a companion to Evidence-Based Statistics by P. Cahusac 
    (2020, ISBN-13 : 978-1119549802).
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: jmvcore (>= 0.8.5), R6, ggplot2, graphics, stats, knitr, car
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
